Protecting your private information is our priority. This Statement of Privacy applies to bestringtoneapps.net and Best Ringtones Apps and governs data collection and usage. For the purposes of this Privacy Policy, unless otherwise noted, all references to Best Ringtones Apps include bestringtoneapps.net, Today’s Hit Ringtones, Best Rap Ringtones, Best Country Ringtones, Best Christian Ringtones, Old Phone Ringtones Popular Ringtones for Google Play and Popular Ringtones for Apple App store. The Best Ringtones Apps are Music, Audio sites and mobile applications. By using the Best Ringtones Apps, you consent to the data practices described in this statement.
Collection of your Personal Information
In order to better provide you with products and services offered on our Site, Best Ringtones Apps may need permission to use personally identifiable information, such as your:
Phone Contacts when selecting ringtones, which allows the device to play a ringtone for your selected contacts.
We can not see your contacts nor do we collect them.
Access to media, storage etc which allows the device to download and play the ringtones.
We have no access to your media nor do we collect it.
We do not collect any personal information about you unless you voluntarily provide it to us. However, you may be required to provide certain personal information to us when you elect to use certain products or services available on the Site. These may include: (a) registering for an account on our Site/Apps; (b) entering a sweepstakes or contest sponsored by us or one of our partners; (c) signing up for special offers from selected third parties; (d) sending us an email message; (e) submitting your credit card or other payment information when ordering and purchasing products and services on our Site. To wit, we will use your information for, but not limited to, communicating with you in relation to services and/or products you have requested from us. We also may gather additional personal or non-personal information in the future.
Use of your Personal Information
Best Ringtones Apps uses Third Party Partners that may collect and use your personal information to operate our website(s)/Apps and deliver the services you have requested.
Best Ringtones Apps uses Third Party Partners that may use your personally identifiable information to inform you of other products or services available from Best Ringtones Apps and its affiliates.
Sharing Information with Third Parties
Best Ringtones Apps does not sell, rent or lease its customer lists to third parties.
Best Ringtones Apps may share data with trusted partners to help perform statistical analysis, send you email or postal mail, provide customer support, or arrange for deliveries. All such third parties are prohibited from using your personal information except to provide these services to Best Ringtones Apps, and they are required to maintain the confidentiality of your information.
Best Ringtones Apps through third partner partners may disclose your personal information, without notice, if required to do so by law or in the good faith belief that such action is necessary to: (a) conform to the edicts of the law or comply with legal process served on Best Ringtones Apps or the site; (b) protect and defend the rights or property of Best Ringtones Apps; and/or (c) act under exigent circumstances to protect the personal safety of users of Best Ringtones Apps, or the public.
Automatically Collected Information
Information about your computer hardware and software may be automatically collected by our Third Party Partners (Google, Facebook and Apple).  This information can include: your IP address, browser type, domain names, access times and referring website addresses. This information is used for the operation of the service, to maintain quality of the service, and to provide general statistics regarding use of the Best Ringtones Apps website.
Children Under Thirteen
Best Ringtones Apps does not knowingly collect personally identifiable information from children under the age of thirteen. If you are under the age of thirteen, you must ask your parent or guardian for permission to use this website.
Changes to this Statement
Best Ringtones Apps reserves the right to change this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you about significant changes in the way we treat personal information by sending a notice to the primary email address specified in your account, by placing a prominent notice on our site, and/or by updating any privacy information on this page. Your continued use of the Site and/or Services available through this Site after such modifications will constitute your: (a) acknowledgment of the modified Privacy Policy; and (b) agreement to abide and be bound by that Policy.
